  "description": "A teaching preset: filterCutoff at 400 Hz. Play it soft and it is a muffled, subterranean drone. Play it hard and the 2000 Hz velocity offset opens it to 2400 Hz — a complete timbral transformation under finger pressure. WEAVE-VI made audible: the low-cutoff expressive design law in single-preset form. The Figure-Eight knot at braidDepth=0.78 provides the topological identity beneath the filter sweep.",
